Start
/ Strict + literal + mismatched bytes → BUILD error (not runtime).
/ Requires fixture photo.png (1x1 transparent PNG). The build step itself
/ must fail with a BuildValidation error; this .test.goal is structured so
/ that the test runner sees the build failure as the success signal.
/
/ The exact test-runner shape for "expects build to fail" is open; if the
/ runner doesn't have it, this test asserts via a wrapper goal that runs
/ the builder and checks the error.
- set %img% = "photo.png" as image/gif strict
